---
alwaysApply: true
---
The Supabase `tasks` table is the canonical task tracker, written via `./task.py`. Never track tasks in local .md files.
- Before starting work: `./task.py start <id>`
- On completion: `./task.py done <id> --by claude_code --note "<what changed>" --ref "<commit>"`
- Discovered work: `./task.py add "<title>" --category <area>`
Run these as actual terminal commands. Do not just describe them.
